{"title":"溪口的黄昏","authors":["力虹"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":5,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"溪口的黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溪口的黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从雪窦山金黄地倾泻而下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在爬满青苔的巨岩间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅起雪瀑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于怀旧的暮色中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇成绵绵剡溪，流向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那镶嵌在溪畔的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象牙般精致的小镇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"憩水桥。乐亭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静卧千年的龟山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在夜曲中沉入冥想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰镐房前的老银杏树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉沉地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉沉地把苍老的虬枝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂向南天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钓鱼台下的鲇鱼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不曾遗忘不曾遗忘那遥远的童趣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落日。古迹。往事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在此时辉映于碧水剡溪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到暮鸦归林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到樵歌唱晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史无情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又最有情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君不见源自雪窦山的剡溪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半个世纪还在绵绵沉吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君不见武岭门已修葺一新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏中阅尽百年兴衰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳下远眺千里归鸿噢！溪口，望断秋水的溪口……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}